sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as ODH Model Controller<br/>Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>InferenceService Controller
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Route as OpenShift Route
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: InferenceService Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>kubectl apply -f inferenceservice.yaml<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission Request<br/>POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>Auth: K8s API client cert (mTLS)
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Admission Response<br/>(Mutated InferenceService)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Notification<br/>InferenceService Created<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Get InferenceService Details<br/>GET /apis/serving.kserve.io/v1beta1/namespaces/{ns}/inferenceservices/{name}<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService Spec

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>POST /apis/route.openshift.io/v1/namespaces/{ns}/routes<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Route Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>POST /apis/monitoring.coreos.com/v1/namespaces/{ns}/servicemonitors<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: ServiceMonitor Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>POST /apis/networking.k8s.io/v1/namespaces/{ns}/networkpolicies<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: NetworkPolicy Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create RBAC Resources<br/>POST /apis/rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1/namespaces/{ns}/roles<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: RBAC Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService Status<br/>PUT /apis/serving.kserve.io/v1beta1/namespaces/{ns}/inferenceservices/{name}/status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService Ready

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: NIM Account Validation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Account CR<br/>kubectl apply -f nimaccount.yaml<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission Request<br/>POST /validate-nim-opendatahub-io-v1-account<br/>Auth: K8s API client cert (mTLS)

    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Read NGC API Key Secret<br/>GET /api/v1/namespaces/{ns}/secrets/{secret-name}<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Webhook: Secret Data

    Webhook->>NGC: Validate NGC API Key<br/>POST /v2/auth/token<br/>Auth: NGC API Key
    NGC-->>Webhook: Validation Response

    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Admission Response<br/>(Account Valid/Invalid)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Notification<br/>Account Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Account Status<br/>PUT /apis/nim.opendatahub.io/v1/namespaces/{ns}/accounts/{name}/status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Template<br/>POST /apis/template.openshift.io/v1/namespaces/{ns}/templates<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: Account Ready

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>K8sAPI: Discover ServiceMonitor<br/>GET /apis/monitoring.coreos.com/v1/servicemonitors<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Prometheus: ServiceMonitor List

    Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape Metrics<br/>GET /metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics Response
